<!--**********************************************************************
    *                                                                    *
    *                        S1000D Issue 2                              *
    *                SGML Document Type Definition                       *
    *                                                                    *
    *                     Release Version 2.2                            *
    *                       Date: 2005-05-01                             *
    *                                                                    *
    * Amendment:-                                                        *
    * 1. Update public identifier date.                                  *
    * 2. CPF 2002-11FR: Update public identifier date of entities %WCNP;,*
    *                   %EXTPARA;.                                       *
    *                   Introduce new public identifier given by entity  *
    *                   %DESCRPTCFG; for descriptive data modules.       *
    *                   Introduce new public identifiers given by        *
    *                   entities %EXTFIG; and %EXTTAB; that replace      *
    *                   entity %EXTFTAB;.                                *
    *                   Introduce new public identifiers given by        *
    *                   entities %EXTWC; and %PARAGRAPHS; that replace   *
    *                   entity %WCNP;.                                   *
    * 3. CPF 2004-25SE: Introduce new public identifier given by entity  *
    *                   %BREX; for the business rules exchange breakdown.*
    * 4. CPF 2004-06SE: Update public identifier date of entities        *
    *                   %EXTDMC;, %CAPGRP;, %COMMON;, %FAULT;, %PROCED;, *
    *                   %SCHEDUL;, %EXTCONT;.                            *
    * 5. CPF 2004-22GB: Update public identifier date of entity          *
    *                   %EXTRESTR;.                                      *
    * 6. CPF 2004-24GB: Update public identifier date of entities        *
    *                   %S1000D; and %EXTAPPL;.                          *
    * 7. CPF 2004-25SE: Introduce new public identifier given by entity  *
    *                   %BREX; for the business rules exchange breakdown.*
    *                   Update public identifier date of entity %EXTSTAT;*
    * 8. CPF 2004-30DE: Introduce public identifier date on entity       *
    *                   %PROJECT;.                                       *
    * 9. CPF 2004-32US: Update public identifier date of entities        *
    *                   %EXTAPPL;; %EXTSTEP;.                            *
    *                   Introduce new entities %APPLINTERACT;,           *
    *                   %APPLSTATIC;, %STEPINTERACT;, %STEPSTATIC;,      *
    *                   %CLOSEREQ;, %PARACONINTERACT;, %PARACONSTATIC;.  *
    * 10.CPF 2004-37DE, 2004-46US:                                       *
    *                   Update public identifier date of entities        *
    *                   %WRNGDATA; and %WRNGFLDS;.                       *
    * 11.CPF 2004-59FR: Update public identifier date of entity %IPD;.   *
    * 12.CPF 2004-61US: Update public identifier date of entity          *
    *                   %INTERACT;.                                      *
    * 13.CPF 2005-06SE: Update public identifier date of entity %EXTPMC;.*
    *                                                                    *
    * Typical invocation:-                                               *
    * <!ENTITY % COMPS                                                   *
    *   PUBLIC "-//S1000D//ENTITIES Component Definitions 20050501//EN" >*
    * %COMPS;                                                            *
    ********************************************************************** -->



<!--**********************************************************************
    * Define Entity %PROJECT; (PROJECT Configuration) containing:- the   *
    * formal public identifier for the Project Configuration public text.*
    ********************************************************************** -->

<!ENTITY % PROJECT
  PUBLIC "-//S1000D//ENTITIES S1000D Project Configuration 20050501//EN" >
<!-- Public identifier date introduced -->  


